# 📷 ASCII CAM v1.2.1

A real-time webcam-to-ASCII art converter that runs entirely in the browser — no server, no dependencies, no install. Drop a photo or point your camera, and watch it render as live ASCII art with full visual controls, effects, and export options.



## ✨ Features

### 🎥 Source Modes
- **Live camera** — real-time webcam feed converted to ASCII at up to 30 fps
- **Image upload** — drop any photo and convert it to ASCII instantly

### 🔤 Character Sets (8 options)
| Set | Characters Used |
|---|---|
| **Detailed** | Dense ramp from space to `@` — most realistic |
| **Simple** | ` .oO0@` — clean and minimal |
| **Blocks** | ` ░▒▓█` — chunky retro feel |
| **Binary** | ` 01` — hacker aesthetic |
| **Matrix** | Japanese katakana + digits |
| **Braille** | Unicode braille dots |
| **Dots** | ` ·∙•` — ultra minimal |
| **Custom** | Type your own characters in light→dark order |

### 🌈 Color Modes (9 options)
| Mode | Description |
|---|---|
| **Real** | Each character colored with the actual pixel color |
| **Green** | Classic terminal green monochrome |
| **Amber** | Retro CRT amber glow |
| **Cyan** | Cool neon cyan wash |
| **Red** | Dramatic red tones |
| **Purple** | Deep purple wash |
| **White** | Pure grayscale |
| **Rainbow** | Hue cycles continuously based on brightness |
| **Custom** | Pick your own dark and bright colors — app interpolates between them |

### 🎛️ Adjustments
- **Font Size** slider — from tiny (maximum detail) to large (chunky retro)
- **Brightness** slider — brighten or darken the source before converting (-100 to +100)
- **Contrast** slider — boost or reduce contrast (-100 to +100)
- **Columns** slider — control character density (30 to 200 columns)
- **Background** slider — from pitch black to near-white
- **FPS Cap** — choose 10, 20, or 30 fps based on device performance

### ✨ Effects
| Effect | Description |
|---|---|
| **GLITCH** | Randomly corrupts ~0.5% of characters each frame for a cyberpunk look |
| **RAIN** | Matrix-style falling characters overlay on top of the feed |
| **HUE ROT** | Continuously rotates hue over time — trippy color cycling |
| **EDGES** | Sobel edge detection — outlines only, like a sketch |
| **CHROM AB** | Chromatic aberration — splits R and B channels for a retro CRT feel |
| **SCANLINE** | CRT scanline overlay — horizontal lines across the output |

### 💾 Export & Share
- **Save PNG** — download the current frame as a high-quality PNG
- **Copy Text** — copy the ASCII art as plain text to clipboard (paste anywhere)
- **Fullscreen** — hide sidebar, go edge-to-edge

### ⌨️ Keyboard Shortcuts
| Key | Action |
|---|---|
| `Space` | Pause / Resume |
| `S` | Save current frame as PNG |
| `F` | Toggle fullscreen |
| `←` | Decrease column count |
| `→` | Increase column count |

### ⚡ Performance
- Auto-pauses rendering when the tab is hidden (Page Visibility API)
- Offscreen canvas for pixel sampling — keeps main thread responsive
- Throttled render loop — only redraws when a new frame is due

