## 🚀 Quick Start

> ⚠️ **Must be served via localhost** — browsers block `getImageData()` on `file://` URLs for security reasons.

### Option 1 — Python (no install required)
```bash
git clone https://github.com/ayuuXploits/ascii-cam.git
cd ascii-cam
python -m http.server 8080
# Open: http://localhost:8080/ascii_cam.html
```

### Option 2 — Node.js
```bash
npx serve .
# Open the URL shown in terminal
```

### Option 3 — VS Code
Install **Live Server** extension → right-click `ascii_cam.html` → **Open with Live Server**

